commit_message:
Reorg existing tempeset test cases

This patch reorganize the existing tempest test cases. The following
changes have been done:
 - Organize API test cases based on Senlin API resource structure,
   e.g. cluster API test cases are now located in api/clusters dir;
 - Redesign verifications of API test cases. We now verify the API
   resp including status code, body, location in header strictly
   following to Senlin API reference;
 - All verifications are now done in specific test cases rather than
   util functions which defined in api/base module;
 - Thinner API client for clustering service is defined for API test;
 - Rework some util functions.

